anner agent generates scapy-based script\n28: - [ ] **AR-037-004-B**: Verify Reporter agent generates human-readable report\n29: - [ ] **AR-037-004-C**: Verify ReAct agent coordinates complete flow\n30: \n31: ### Task AR-037-T007: Verify configuration handling\n32: - [ ] **AR-037-005-A**: Verify default configuration values\n33: - [ ] **AR-037-005-B**: Verify environment variable overrides\n34: - [ ] **AR-037-005-C**: Verify required env vars validation\n35: \n36: ## Phase 2: Container & Deployment\n37: \n38: ### Task AR-037-T008: Verify Dockerfile\n39: - [ ] **AR-037-007-A**: Verify Dockerfile uses Python base, sets PYTHONPATH, exposes port 8000\n40: - [ ] **AR-037-007-B**: Verify SDK vendoring in build context\n41: \n42: ### Task AR-037-T009: Verify Kubernetes deployment\n43: - [ ] **AR-037-008-A**: Verify deployment manifest structure\n44: - [ ] **AR-037-008-B**: Verify environment variable wiring in deployment\n45: \n46: ## Phase 3: SDK Integration & Workflow\n47: \n48: ### Task AR-037-T010: Verify SDK integration\n49: - [ ] **AR-037-009-A**: Verify SDK import (`CodeInterpreterClient`)\n50: - [ ] **AR-037-009-B**: Verify context manager usage with ControlPlaneClient\n51: - [ ] **AR-037-009-C**: Verify SDK exception handling\n52: \n53: ### Task AR-037-T011: Verify complete analysis workflow\n54: - [ ] **AR-037-010-A**: Verify complete analysis flow (upload → script → execute → report)\n55: - [ ] **AR-037-010-B**: Verify invalid PCAP file handling\n56: - [ ] **AR-037-010-C**: Verify large file handling\n57: \n58: ## Phase 4: Documentation & Tests\n59: \n60: ### Task AR-037-T012: Verify README documentation\n61: - [ ] **AC018**: Verify README.md contains usage instructions\n62: \n63: ### Task AR-037-T013: Run test suite\n64: - [ ] Run existing tests in `tests/test_pcap_analyzer.py`\n65: - [ ] Verify all test cases pass\n66: - [ ] Add any missing test coverage\n67: \n68: ## Acceptance Criteria Checklist\n69: \n70: - [ ] AC001: `example/pcap-analyzer/` directory cont